      <span>Enterprise document management</span>
    </li>
    <li class="flex items-center space-x-3">
      <BoxIcon name="check" class="flex-shrink-0 w-5 h-5 text-green-500 dark:text-green-400" />
      <span>24/7 dedicated support</span>
    </li>
    <li class="flex items-center space-x-3">
      <BoxIcon name="check" class="flex-shrink-0 w-5 h-5 text-green-500 dark:text-green-400" />
